<a name="newsitem1021997877,81608,"></a> <p style="margin-left: 8; margin-right: 8"><b><font face="Verdana" size="3" color="#DDDD00">Tech Support/Live Chat Closed For The Holiday</font><font color="#DDDD00"><br>
      </font>
