 <p style="margin-left: 8; margin-right: 8"><b><font face="Verdana" size="3" color="#DDDD00">Legends "Reservation" System</font><font color="#DDDD00"><br>
      </font>
      </b><font face="Arial" size="2"><font color="#FFC164"><small>10:01 EST - <a href="mailto:hermana@gameznet.com">Hermana</a></small></font><br>
      <br>Recently on the Legends Server there was an announcement about a <a href="http://legends.everquest.station.sony.com/newsview.jsp?o=43132">Target Reservation System</a>, that basically reserves Targets for guilds and limits the server on it's ability to be FFA.  I found this very interesting, considering most server and the GM's on them don't adhere to this type of system.  It should be interesting to see how it works out.</font></p>
